<title type="html"><![CDATA[8/15(Thu.)3 Ways to Deal With Missing Teeth/You Don't Find Happiness, You Create It | Katarina Blom(Host:William)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=307&amp;p=323#p323"><![CDATA[
8/15(Thu.)3 Ways to Deal With Missing Teeth/You Don't Find Happiness, You Create It | Katarina Blom | TEDxGöteborg(Host:William)<br /><br />Article 1:3 Ways to Deal With Missing Teeth<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://northoaksdental.com/blog/3-ways-to-deal-with-missing-teeth/">https://northoaksdental.com/blog/3-ways ... ing-teeth/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Discussion<br />1. The toothache sometimes happen at night. Did you have this kind of experiences? How did you deal with it ? <br />2. Do you have any tips to protect your teeth ? <br />3. If you have missing tooth what do you plan to do ? <br />4. Do you know the differences between the dental bridge and tooth implant ? <br />5. Did you have tooth implant or your friends have ? Please share with us ?<br /><br />Article 2:You Don't Find Happiness, You Create It | Katarina Blom | TEDxGöteborg<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://youtu.be/9DtcSCFwDdw">https://youtu.be/9DtcSCFwDdw</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Discussion<br />1. Do you love what you are doing ? <br />2. Do you often do little things to make you happier ? <br />3. How to love yourself first ? <br />4. How to stop worrying and keep it moving ? <br />5. Happiness is a habit. Do you agree with it ?<br /><br />Suggested Agenda<br />7:00 p.m. --7:30 p.m. free talk <br />7:30 p.m. --8:10 p.m. first topic discussion <br />8:10 p.m. --8:40 p.m. Presentation (All participants are invited)<br />8:40 p.m.-- 9.:15 p.m. second topic discussion <br />9:15 p.m.-- 9:30 p.m. Presentation<br /><br />speaker time : 2 minutes for each speaker<br />host time : 3 minutes<br /><br />The meeting place of Thursday:<br />丹堤咖啡寶慶店：台北市延平南路107號2F (上樓右邊第三區塊)<br />捷運資訊： 近台北捷運–西門站 (4號出口步行約2分鐘，康是美隔壁)<br />丹堤低消: NT$80元<br />最自由的全英文會話聚會,前三次不用交會費,加入會員終生會費NT$500，帶著開放與熱情來學英文<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=12531">Danny Lin</a> — Thu Aug 08, 2019 10:08 pm</p><hr />
